high_descs: Turn right and reach the shelf under the TV on the right sidetable.
Pick up the knife from the top of the shelf.
Turn around and walk to the couch across the room.
Cut the bread on the couch into slices with the knife.
Head to the cabinet counter on the right.
Open the second door on the left and put the knife in the cabinet.
Turn around and walk to the sofa.
Pick up a slice of bread from the couch.
Turn right to head to the fridge on the right.
Cool the slice of bread in the fridge and take it out.
Turn left to face the microwave.
Put the slice of bread in the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Put the cold slice of Bread in the Microwave.

high_descs: Turn right and go towards the TV on the sidetable.
Pick up the knife from the shelf beneath the TV.
Turn around and go towards the large white couch.
Slice the bread on the couch.
Turn right and go straight ahead to the cabinet.
Place the knife into the cabinet.
Return to the loaf of bread.
Pick up a slice of bread.
Turn right again and head towards the cabinet, then right again to the fridge.
Place the bread in the fridge, let it cool, then remove it.
Go to the microwave to the left of the fridge.
Place the bread in the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Slice a loaf of Bread, cool one slice in a fridge, and place that slice in a Microwave.

high_descs: Make a left and walk to the sidetable.
Pick up the knife that is on the entertainment center.
Take the bread and walk over to the sofa.
Use the knife to slice the bread that is on top of the sofa.
Walk to the cabinet and open the door.
Put the knife away in the cabinet.
Walk back to the sofa, where the sliced bread is.
Pick up one slice of the bread.
Take the bread with you to the fridge.
Put the bread in the fridge and, let it get cold then remove it.
Take the bread to the microwave.
Open the door and put the bread in the microwave.
anns.task_desc: moving a slice of Bread from one place to Microwave.
